<gp_project_root ver="1">
  <gallery />
  <favorites>
    <tool name="CalculateField" type="function" toolboxalias="management" gallery_group="Project Favorites">
      <displayname>Calculate Field</displayname>
      <description>Calculates the values of a field for a feature class, feature layer, or raster.</description>
    </tool>
    <tool name="Buffer" type="function" toolboxalias="analysis" gallery_group="Project Favorites">
      <displayname>Buffer</displayname>
      <description>Creates buffer polygons around input features to a specified distance.</description>
    </tool>
    <tool name="Near" type="function" toolboxalias="analysis" gallery_group="Project Favorites">
      <displayname>Near</displayname>
      <description>Calculates distance and additional proximity information between the input features and the closest feature in another layer or feature class.</description>
    </tool>
    <tool name="SpatialJoin" type="function" toolboxalias="analysis" gallery_group="Project Favorites">
      <displayname>Spatial Join</displayname>
      <description>Joins attributes from one feature to another based on the spatial relationship. The target features and the joined attributes from the join features are written to the output feature class.</description>
    </tool>
    <tool name="Intersect" type="function" toolboxalias="analysis" gallery_group="Project Favorites">
      <displayname>Intersect</displayname>
      <description>Computes a geometric intersection of the input features. Features or portions of features that overlap in all layers or feature classes will be written to the output feature class.</description>
    </tool>
  </favorites>
</gp_project_root>
